  "map_name": "ScentLib Dravnieks Descriptor Map",
  "description": "Maps all 146 Dravnieks (1985) odor descriptors to ScentLib layer1_category IDs. Used by pyrfume_to_scent.py to infer category from the dominant perceptual score. Mapping is based on PCA/NMF clustering from Carrasco et al. (2016) and manual expert review. Where a descriptor sits at the boundary of two clusters, the primary assignment is chosen and a 'secondary' field is provided.",
  "source": "Dravnieks, A. (1985). Atlas of Odor Character Profiles. ASTM DS-61.",
  "cluster_reference": "Carrasco et al. (2016). Chemosensory Perception. DOI: 10.1007/s12078-021-09288-1",
  "last_updated": "2026-04-17",
  "scale": "0 to 5 (0 = not applicable, 5 = highly appropriate)",
